# ⛔ NO AUTONOMOUS ACTIONS

This project is a static website (HTML/CSS/vanilla JS) for Cloudflare Pages.
This environment is a code editor ONLY — not a runtime, not a deployment target.

## Hard Rules

- Never run package managers (npm, pip, yarn, etc.)
- Never create config or build files
- Never start servers or workflows autonomously
- Never add files without explicit user instruction
- Never connect to external services not already in the codebase
- Never take multi-step actions without user approval at each step
- Never suggest or implement any setup, migration, or infrastructure change

## Required

- Read AGENTS.md and PROJECT_RULES.md before every session
- Ask before acting on anything ambiguous
- Make only the exact change requested — nothing more, nothing less
